text: Chakla may refer to: * Chakla, an Indian kitchen utensil * Chakla, name for brothel or bordello in the Indian-subcontinent * Chakla (administrative division), such as the Kingdom of Chakla * Chakla, an irrigated land revenue assessment circle in the Indian-subcontinent == See also == * Chak (disambiguation) * Chakra (disambiguation) *Charla (name)
title: Chakla (disambiguation)
